{"tid":787313,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)死侍2 雷神決戰塔利班 致命報酬","createTime":"2018-08-20T14:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T19:38:18.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bd202adf1beeb6061d5e26b67952aefa695be48c","tid":787313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=51JnEPTXRju7sY6J5sQGep4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=cdc1c8b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=51JnEPTXRju7sY6J5sQGep4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5bfe852e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=51JnEPTXRju7sY6J5sQGep4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=36c59eb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d0/12_Strong_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd0%2F12_Strong_Poster.jpg&h=46aa699b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c9/Paycheck_filmposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc9%2FPaycheck_filmposter.jpg&h=c4a8f49c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.<img src=\"https://img.itw01.com/images/2018/04/01/02/2413_uLvtC6_VZNSWED.jpg!r1024x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.itw01.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F02%2F2413_uLvtC6_VZNSWED.jpg%21r1024x0.jpg&h=c1edbe40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述在九一一襲擊事件過後，美國發動反恐戰爭前，事先派遣了美國陸軍特種部隊綠扁帽第5特種作戰群，被派往阿富汗執行先遣作戰，並扶持阿布都&middot;拉希德&middot;杜斯塔姆將軍共同對抗塔利班<br />\n<br />\n3.一個專門以逆向工程竊取最新技術的著名工程師，每當任務完成時，有關的全部記憶將被消除，酬勞則匯到他指定的銀行帳戶。在完成一次歷時三年的任務後，發現自己主動放棄高達千萬美元的酬勞，得到的只有一個裝著鎖匙、車票、髮膠等小東西的牛皮紙袋，隨後更被聯邦調查局調查及被不明人士追殺。他必須尋找蛛絲馬跡來找回記憶，揭開在背後醜陋的真相<br />\n<br />\n10 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=51JnEPTXRju7sY6J5sQGep4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=281085bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=51JnEPTXRju7sY6J5sQGep4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9e29ff06\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60aab0e336722b6f9c78ad379aadea1ac03253f","tid":787313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e099c5bf32a6deb5663007571e7